{
  "stem": "22892.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was-- I mean, there was-- this farm was very much an isolated-- I mean, there was a-- like a forest-- was a pine forest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They owned ten hectares of forest, and I don't know how many acres that is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a pretty good size.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were-- so nobody saw me going there, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were just afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had to go on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said I couldn't stay too much longer here, he says.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I took off, and I just wandered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To day, I was mostly going from area to area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sometime I would just go into a house that I think maybe was fairly safe and get some food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and at night, I would sneak in some barn, stay at somebody's barn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't know whether I was there or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The next day, I just walked again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was still in the fall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In wandering from place to place, I, I went into this farmer and, you know, wanted-- I hoped we-- they would give me some food, and they did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, you know, not far from here there's this area where there's maybe 200 or 300 Jews, he says, working there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, maybe that's a good place for you to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they won't kill them anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the way he said that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, I thought there was just nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the Jews are killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was sort of surprising to me that he mentioned that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I kept going there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And came up with, with like a, a top of the hill there's this huge-- it's almost like a castle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a Polish count at one time lived there, and I don't know how many acres.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
